{"tid":859887,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：鼓吹或說港獨是選項大家可自決都觸碰一國底線","createTime":"2018-10-13T01:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T02:20:36.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"30e3625513d9993c1ebd40821b91f5cd020335f0","tid":859887,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T01:57:42.000Z","msg":"特首：鼓吹或說港獨是選項大家可自決都觸碰一國底線<br />\n2018-10-13 HKT 09:54<br />\n 分享工具\t facebook  twitter<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥在一個電台節目提到，港獨或自決是觸碰「一國」的底線，並不存在政治包容的空間。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，雖然她曾經提到越多政治包容，得到的夥伴越多，但這是有一個前設就是不觸碰一國的底線。<br />\n<br />\n她又說這條底線在一國兩制之中，在基本法內清晰反映出來，她作為行政長官是有雙負責制，既向香港負責，亦要向中央人民政府負責，不能觸碰「一國」的底線，任何鼓吹港獨，或說港獨是選項，大家可以自決，全部都是觸碰底線，並不存在政治包容的空間。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，她可以息事寧人，但後果是有人會變本加厲，她覺得些事是不能迴避，應該是要有勇氣去向社會講清楚，是一件怎樣的事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1422814-20181013.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1422814-20181013.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=QvySEdzGX266GlvRhfVdURFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=c785f024\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1422814-20181013.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e6038999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1422814-20181013.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"0c72559ddb41a039b71545204cb97c442ca28612","tid":859887,"uid":4285,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T01:58:44.000Z","msg":"廿鳩幾條底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f2bebfae47ec7084c8e5135e36fdcb67534d89","tid":859887,"uid":4942,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T01:59:30.000Z","msg":"條底線就快高到上天 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9198f07521972813d41b694489eeb2367ec51843","tid":859887,"uid":26329,"like":5,"dislike